whatDoILike: What do I like to do?
aboutContent: Welcome to my personal site... I made it about 9 months ago, and I'm a new woman, so it's possible that everything written in these pages is a little outdated. Now, I'm in my 3rd year in college, so I've started taking my education courses :) I'm pretty happy with my choice in career, even though the program at my school annoys me so often.
whatDoILikeContent:
Well, I love web design. I love those sites that experiment with the medium. I've also seen a few "digital gardens" online, collections of things that the creator appreciates. I love the idea, and the digital garden sites made by others inspire me so much that I made my own.

It's organized like an apartment. A pretty strange apartment, since I'm not an artist and I wanted the elements to line up nicely to organize with a grid.
